OOC: I just got back from Stratton, Vermont(Awesome skiing trip!).  I just 
read a ton of messages, so forgive me if i get anything wrong and correct me. 
 Jason, Tigerhawk is with Airazor heading back to the CF.

:::Wheeljack/Starscream/Bludgeon/Obsidian/The 
Destrocons/Falcon/Snare/Sideswipe/Time Warp/Atma/Psuedo:::

::Wheeljack programmed his drones, and actvated the defense mechanism.  The 
drones ran around for awhile, but they were all eventually taken out by the 
torpedos and homing missles.  Wheeljack smiles from ear to ear::
Wheeljack: SUCCESS!  We should report this to Zardus!
~~~~~
::Obsidian and Bludgeon hear Drillbit's transmission and head to Hell Beasts 
base. Starscream finds Drillbit::
Starscream: Im here Drillbit, buddy.
::He tunnels with him and reaches Hell Beast base.  Bludgeon and Obsidian 
arrive around the same time::
~~~~~
::My Destrons hear Magmatron and transform to their flight modes and head to 
Hell Beasts base::
~~~~~
::Sideswipe gets hit by one of Squawkbox's shots, but escapes the other. He 
transforms to robot mode, but by the time his guns are ready Squawktalk and 
Beastbox had left::
~~~~~
::Time Warp is just as ticked as Airbomber::
Time Warp: Its obvious that Infectra isnt here! Lets get out of here before 
we get killed!
~~~~~
::Atma and Psuedo watch Gramps' death, when they hear Technosis. They run 
after her::
Psuedo: Gramps is dead.
Atma: I think Termitron killed him.

--part1_a7.c0bef0b.27cb0512_boundary
